Full Description: ahatis is the trusted advisor to businesses looking for smarter ways to implement technology solutions to real business problems. We take our clients’ businesses as seriously as a key internal executive and we are equally committed to your success. In order to provide exceptional value, the focus at ahatis is on why, not what. We look deep into the business to find the root causes of business issues because it’s there that a solution will have the greatest impact. With a technology agnostic approach that adapts to our clients needs, ahatis is expert at identifying and implementing the most cost-effective tech stack that will drive the results our clients seek.   Depending on your needs, we will:   ·      Advise when you need advice ·      Build when you need to add a custom capability ·      Recommend and implement existing solutions when they are the best option ·      Staff with people with the skill set and experience you require ·      Create and support enterprise solutions ·      Listen to what you want and deliver what you need   Together, we’ll find a smarter way. Many of our engagements lead us to build software products that solve for common issues across CPG, Finance, Health Care and other industries. From our ROSE trade management solution for CPG companies to Highland, the market's only industrialized data conversion platform, we deliver capabilities and not just technology.

Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: Mobilestead provides solutions that enable hotels to integrate mobile guest services into their existing infrastructure.  The user friendly and intuitive applications revolutionize the availability of information and increase the utility of the hotel experience. A tourist usually starts their hotel stay with asking the hotel concierge frequently asked questions such as "Which restaurant do you recommend?," "Which museum or Broadway show do I go to?" The secondary question to follow is always "How do I get there?" The mobile device provides the tourist with virtual concierge services to answer all those questions on demand. The guest will have access to this information on the go and make instantaneous reservations all from their device. The hotel is able to present all their in-house offerings such as restaurants, spa and entertainment services and facilitate the reservation or sale immediately. By integrating the Mobilestead System with the existing PMS (Property Management System) the hotel is able to offer basic services such as express check-out, wake-up call requests, housekeeping and bill display via the mobile device.  Mobilestead presents a platform to deliver 3rd party applications which are crucial to the tourist through one integrated medium.
